L1 Substrate Stateless LLM inference GPT/Claude/Gemini inference calls CPU
L2 Memory/Ledger Persistent storage and audit trail Ledger L, ThoughtObject archive Storage / WAL
L3 Cognitive Data Structured cognitive state StateVector SV, ThoughtObjects TO RAM + Data Structures
L4 Decision/Gate Invariant-governed action approval Gate G, SC computation, OASA loop Kernel / Scheduler
L5 Governance Ethics and constraint enforcement Invariant Set I, Mirror daemon OS Security Layer
L6 Narrative/Id. Identity coherence and distillation Narrative, distillation pipeline User Space
L7 Myth/Meaning Symbolic compression and doctrine Hogge compression, doctrine pages Culture / Org Memory
